    <articleReference>
      <Value><![CDATA[Lasers in Medical Science May 2012, Volume 27, Issue 3, pp 559-566]]></Value>
    </articleReference>
    <articleTitle>
      <Value><![CDATA[Efficacy of low-level laser therapy in the management of pain, facial swelling, and postoperative trismus after a lower third molar extraction. A preliminary study]]></Value>
